# Sample personas are public: Claude Code reads CLAUDE.md (not AGENTS.md), so
# the two-claudes-debating personas must ship a CLAUDE.md (see ADR-049). These
# negations exempt them from the repo-wide CLAUDE.md ignore above.
!examples/two-claudes-debating/claude-a/CLAUDE.md
!examples/two-claudes-debating/claude-b/CLAUDE.md

